    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000085/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """The course of advanced statistics aimed to overlook various aspects of modern statistics, amongst which
Bayes inferences
inverse problems
stochastics modeling - linear regression, clustering task
Monte Carlo methods
temporal series
Ising model
The course aims to provide a solid theoretical foundation for each of its topics, while also offering practical experience through case studies, where students will implement the algorithms and methods covered in class."""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/aurelien.decelle%40upm.es> ;
